      = link_to "#" do
        Edit
  .chat-main__message-list
    .chat-main__message-list__message
      .chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box
        %p.chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box__message-poster
          mitsu
        %p.chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box__post-date
          2020/06/15(Mon) 12:34:55  
      %p.chat-main__message-list__message__lower-box__message-text
        四角さん資格取得おめでとう
    .chat-main__message-list__message    
      .chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box
        %p.chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box__message-poster
          四角
        %p.chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box__post-date
          2020/06/15(Mon) 12:36:55  
      %p.chat-main__message-list__message__lower-box__message-text
        ありがとうございます！
    .chat-main__message-list__message    
      .chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box
        %p.chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box__message-poster
          三角
        %p.chat-main__message-list__message__upper-box__post-date
          2020/06/15(Mon) 12:38:55  
      %p.chat-main__message-list__message__lower-box__message-text
        おめでとう！！    
  .chat-main__message-form
    %form.chat-main__message-form__new-message
      .input-box
        %input{type: "text", class: "input-box__text", placeholder: "type a message"}
        %label{class: "input-box__image"}
          = icon("far", "image")
          %input{type: "file", class: "input-box__image__file"}
      %input{class: "submit-btn", type: "submit", name: "commit", value: "Send"}
